01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda568293725858272c526e48fb848fd911d32e1","tid":1745136,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"poly某同學 : 希望你地俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Sdhr7X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Sdhr7X.png&h=b4b8b6d1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}